{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "首輪競賽", "storyInfo": "陳和林雨霞的配合並不算好，兩人心知肚明，並決定分頭行動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$fesedm_intro", "key": "$fesedm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好強，太強了！鼠膽龍威隊，在被三支隊伍聯手圍攻的局面之下，輕鬆將他們擊退！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，林女俠在戰鬥中使用的究竟是什麼能力？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "導播，切一下重播！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.5, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只見林雨霞的手在身邊房屋的玻璃窗上輕輕一抹，玻璃如同熔化了一般緩慢消失。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而後，她的手中出現了一把鋒利的刀刃，這把刀刃幾近無色，只有反射陽光帶來的細微光芒證明著它確實存在。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一回終於看清楚了，林女俠居然能夠將玻璃轉化為武器，這真是令人意想不到的能力！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到林女俠不光武藝高超，還有這般精彩的源石技藝！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，不過Missy，林小姐這是什麼能力？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和鼠王一樣，其實她也是在操縱沙子，只是方向不太一樣。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從小能隨隨便便地把沙子變成玻璃什麼的，我經常問她要來玩。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢，懂了，確實，玻璃也是用沙子做的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，我聽說鼠王可以用沙子搞出沙塵暴，林小姐行不行啊？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，不過我猜她就算會，也不會喜歡那麼做。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，林小姐看起來不像是喜歡大開大合的類型。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林女俠那防不勝防的源石技藝，配合陳女俠精準的銃法，還有埃內斯托先生的補漏，一次完美的視覺盛宴！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何，潘喬先生，您認為這次的勝利會屬於這支隊伍嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這支隊伍個人能力很強，不過配合還欠缺火候。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，確實，在這樣的比賽中，如果過分強調個人能力，可是會被其他人盯上然後排除掉的。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史一再地向我們證明，只有團結才能夠取得最後的勝利！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個老頭眼光很尖啊，一眼就看出來老陳和林小姐現在最大的問題。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，這兩個人，老陳嘛，跟你搭檔慣了至少知道配合，不過她完全不知道林雨霞是怎麼打的，自己又用的不是最拿手的劍，束手束腳的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於林雨霞，這個女人就根本不知道配合這兩個字是怎麼寫的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看好幾次她差點把老陳也傷到了，全靠老陳反應夠快閃了過去。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笑死我了，不知道的還以為她們倆配合無間呢。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個叫埃內斯托的倒也聰明，根本沒往兩個人身邊靠。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然啊，他有幾條命都不夠用。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯啊，Missy，觀察力越來越好了，我還以為我要給你講解一下呢。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了接過陳暉潔的位置我也是很努力的好不好。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可從沒懷疑過這一點，只是沒想到Missy你的進步這麼快，真不錯。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別一副老前輩的樣子在那感慨了，小心我扣你薪水。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，那可千萬別，您老大人有大量，別跟我一個小卒一般計較。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，這還像話。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你還真別說，看她們這配合，讓我有點想起剛認識老陳的時候了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她那時就這樣？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡，反過來，那時的她，和現在的林小姐差不多吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是讓那時的她和現在的林小姐組隊，那恐怕真的打著打著她們兩個就打起來了，哈哈。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的玻璃刀好幾次差點割到我。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的水彈準頭也不怎麼樣。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來不只是情感上，戰術上我們也不適合組隊。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很有說服力的結論，還是分頭行動吧。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這樣吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我知道兩位彼此無法配合，不過既然組成了隊伍，那還是儘量像一支隊伍一樣行動吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前也說過，比賽途中無法通信，而且兩位不僅要找赤金，還想要調查可能存在的危險分子。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然兩位的個人能力很強，但炎國不是有句話叫做——不怕一萬，只怕萬一。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我的提議是，無論有沒有獲得赤金，我們一小時在這裡碰一次頭，如何？", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有一方沒來，另一方見機行事。", "name": "埃內斯托"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒意見。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，兩位願意配合那再好不過，那就這麼辦吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我先走一步。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林小姐走得真快......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳小姐，你是打算單獨行動，還是讓我和你一起行動。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用為我和她考慮太多，我和她都不是為了賭氣能什麼都不管不顧的人，對的不會說成錯的，該做的還是會做。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......平心而論，即使沒有合不合適的問題，分頭行動也是第一輪比賽中非常常見的做法。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，我們只有三個人，我認為是沒有三人都分散出去的必要的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我還是跟你一起行動吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以。走吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}